  "description": {
    "S": "Crying Tiger is an iconic Isan (Northeastern Thai) dish of smoky, charred steak served with nam jim jaew, an explosively flavorful dipping sauce packed with toasted rice powder, chili, lime, and fish sauce. The name comes from the idea that the steak is so good, even a tiger would cry for more. This is an absolute crowd-pleaser."
  },
